Macro.name: MO_BCD_TFIXARRAY(CT, T)
Macro.value: template <TInt size> class MO_CM_DECLARE CT : public TFixArray<T, size>{ public: CT(){ } CT(const T* pValues, TInt length){ this->Append(pValues, length); } CT(const MPtrC<T>& ptr){ this->Append(ptr); } public: void operator=(const MPtrC<T>& ptr){ this->Assign(ptr); } };

Macro.name: MO_BCD_TFIXSTRING16(C, P)
Macro.value: class MO_CM_DECLARE C : public P{ public: C(){ } C(const C& value) : P(value){ } C(TChar16C* pValue, TInt length=-1) : P(pValue, length){ } C(const MString16PtrC& value) : P(value){ } public: void operator=(TChar16C* pValue){ this->Assign(pValue); } void operator=(const C& value){ this->Assign(value.MemoryC(), value.Length()); } void operator=(const MString16PtrC& value){ this->Assign(value.MemoryC(), value.Length()); } };

Macro.name: MO_BCD_TFIXSTRING32(C, P)
Macro.value: class MO_CM_DECLARE C : public P{ public: C(){ } C(const C& value) : P(value){ } C(TChar32C* pValue, TInt length=-1) : P(pValue, length){ } C(const MString32PtrC& value) : P(value){ } public: void operator=(TChar32C* pValue){ this->Assign(pValue); } void operator=(const C& value){ this->Assign(value.MemoryC(), value.Length()); } void operator=(const MString32PtrC& value){ this->Assign(value.MemoryC(), value.Length()); } };

Macro.name: MO_BCD_TFIXSTRING8(C, P)
